00:04:59,706 --> 00:05:00,845
Ji Eun.

53
00:05:02,076 --> 00:05:03,375
Čo sa to deje?

54
00:05:03,375 --> 00:05:05,216
Nepribližujte sa!

55
00:05:05,216 --> 00:05:07,616
Choďte preč. Nepribližujte sa!

56
00:05:07,915 --> 00:05:09,355
Čo sa to deje?

57
